{"tid":52450,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「嚇撚死」有圖：琴晚兩點幾，搭亡命van由旺角番官塘","createTime":"2016-12-24T05:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T05:49:13.000Z","uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa47f944457c85f5076b5f6d870efd0c869a17b","tid":52450,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"小弟有一day由旺角返屋企，由於太夜，因此要搭亡命小巴<br />\n在小巴上坐在司機後的一對情侶，在上車後不斷鬧交。<br />\n女的不斷鬧男是仆x，而男則鬧女的是死八婆。<br />\n經過15分鐘的「口部對戰」，男的終於忍不到，講了一句粗口。<br />\n<br />\n男︰「正臭x，講極都唔明，正臭x（x為粗口也）」<br />\n女︰「如果真系臭，咁你又『奶』」<br />\n<br />\n突然全車靜晒，司機減速駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n各位男士要講粗口鬧人要三思<br />\n免得把生活公諸於世。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/133837_e9833a0dcb0676cd78551df70a63a76b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F133837_e9833a0dcb0676cd78551df70a63a76b.jpg&h=7e5647e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ae6d31c8e77eadfd1a62f3cad616eba0aaba629","tid":52450,"uid":6290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15957b2355981e228dd351de40dfea0cc4e4d23","tid":52450,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"究竟有幾多個版本"},{"pid":"d6c6bb7ef75e0953df74382f782d4e391ff9b794","tid":52450,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"加幾隻字就當自己原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cd6605738cfeaf05d63df759c51705f5dd00bf","tid":52450,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加幾隻字就當自己原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到話原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 